&lt;li&gt;Provide on-set leadership in collaboration with Production Supervisor, production team, and&amp;nbsp;camera crew.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with editors from pre-production to delivery, including providing feedback on&amp;nbsp;edits, assist conceiving of graphics and on-screen text.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze performance data, and use data to create incremental video optimizations that scale.&lt;/li&gt;
