&lt;li&gt;Experience writing and directing in fast-paced, digital-first environments (UGC, branded content, social, or creator economy ideal)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional concepting and storytelling skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mastery of on-set creative leadership and understanding of how to successfully direct celebrity partners and actors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to formulate strategies on how to market petcare products in fresh, creative and different ways.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of direct response marketing.&lt;/li&gt;
