&lt;li&gt;1-2 years in a customer service role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 year customer service in a Contact Center setting (preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency using windows-based applications, Google Suite, and Microsoft Office software (preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of call center systems and/or workflows (preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
