&lt;li&gt;Perform audits of web analytics implementations and make recommendations to ensure accurate tracking is in place.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with our internal affiliate team and/or directly with the affiliate and agency partners who advertise for us and make sure that our strict KPIs are met.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
