&lt;li&gt;Increase revenue generated on branded websites by increasing customer engagement, cart sizes/AOV, frequency of purchases, account creation, and subscription-opt-in.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with development, brand managers, and design teams to maintain an efficient pipeline of ideas that stay congruent with brand messaging, strategy, and goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continually look for ways to improve branded site experience, including but not limited to the customer account portal, subscription management, and PDP/PLP optimizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with UX to assess and enhance website performance, including site speed, user experience, navigation, etc to optimize customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create monthly and quarterly reports based on test results and other ongoing initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
