&lt;li&gt;Drive A/B testing strategy with an understanding of statistical significance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data-driven and results-minded.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work efficiently within a fast-paced, results-driven environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to independently organize and implement several multi-step projects at once.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic HTML/CCS proficiency a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creative thinking, excellent organization skills and high attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to build strong relationships with proactive follow-up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have a robust willingness to learn, support, and actively participate in the growth of the business.&lt;/li&gt;
